About Selecto

For three years now our company unites bright minds which create unique IT-solutions with top notch design that can't leave anyone indifferent. A professional approach to business, combined with broad experience of our developers and designers are what help us success at bringing clients' ideas to life in the best way possible.
By choosing us you're choosing a team of qualified and result driven individuals dedicated to delivering high quality and competitive products. We're not just a one-off contractor. We strive to become a part of your team and business partner.

Selecto is Global

In three years of our work we have successfully completed over 60 projects for clients from over 15 countries.
  • 60 + Projects

Our Principles

  • Healthy work environment
    People are the most valuable asset a company has. After all, the success of the company depends on its employees. So, we made sure to create a comfortable work environment, where employees feel free and don't take their job as a chore.
  • Strong customer relationship
    Regardless of the distance and time zone, we strive to become a part of your team and a reliable partner in bringing your ideas to life. We believe that great results can be achieved through a strong relationship with the client, so regular check points and Skype calls with our client is an essential part of daily agenda.
  • Continuous growth and learning
    The path to success lies through continuous learning and self-improvement. We strongly encourage and support our employees in their desire to grow as professionals. We're curious and eager to explore new technologies and take on complex projects as it helps us deliver superb services.
